                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-921" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES COX</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Watt, a pawnbroker, in Ex<lb></lb>mouth-street. I produce these articles which were pawned on the 4th, 5th, and 6th of May, by the prisoner—he pawned the bolster—I cannot be certain of the others—but it was a man.</p>
